'''Ahmad Shah Abouwi''' was an [[Afghanistan]] field hockey player, who competed at the [[1956 Summer Olympic Games]]. He played in all three matches.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ab/ahmad-shah-abouwi-1.html Sports-Reference Profile]</ref>

