An '''anti-suicide blanket''' is a tear-resistant blanket that is used to prevent a [[hospital]]ized, [[incarcerated]] or otherwise detained individual from forming a [[noose]] to commit [[suicide]].  The blanket is typically made of simple and sturdily quilted nylon or similarly reinforced material.  The stiffness of the blanket makes it impossible to roll or fold without continuously applied pressure.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.securingcosmos.com/shopexd.asp?id=3490|title=Safety Blanket.|date=September 2007|accessdate=September 4, 2007| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070929143406/http://www.securingcosmos.com/shopexd.asp?id=3490| archivedate= 29 September 2007 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>  The same material is used for the [[anti-suicide smock]].

